<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201201/4be74f890d7f4102b12ce0f740845ffd.png" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">（图片来源：网络截图）</span></img></p>
